            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>If the President...</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"What is the patriotism of a man worth who spends his time in impeaching
                    the loyalty of his neighbors and is yet very careful to keep out of the ranks
                    himself?"</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Criticizes those who chide Democrats as secessionists yet refrain from
                    joining the army.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
